A 36-YEAR-OLD woman was arrested after having sex on a balcony. The video of the couple, caught having sex on a balcony in Hong Kong, has since gone viral. According to the Daily Star, cops said they discovered the clip after it was circulating on the Internet, and have classified the case as a public indecency act. READ: RISE IN PUBLIC TLOF TLOF CASES! The woman was arrested in Sau Mau Ping on Tuesday and has now been released on bail. It was not clear if the man was also arrested, but cops said they could not rule out more arrests. The couple received mixed reception online – while some have slammed their act, many others are sympathetic. One disgruntled online commenter slammed the scene as a “diminishing of morals”. However, another different concerned user claimed: “You can’t even [have sex] in private places.”